It is great opportunity to work on development of next generation Infotainment system for one of the largest American OEMs. You will be able to gain unprecedented knowledge in integrating the most advanced technologies on the market and be a part of ongoing mobility revolution in Automotive world.
 
This role assumes to design, develop, and implement next generation IVI technologies with specialization: Edge Tech Function focusing on Machine Learning and Artificial Intelligence.
 
 Responsibilities: 
 
 Defining Specification for Edge Tech 
 Lead the specifications development for IoT Edge AI/ML platform/solution for the next generation multimedia 
 Work with internal and external teams/suppliers to elaborate and finalize specs 
 Create criteria and evaluation matrix for candidate products/technologies and recommend solution 
 Identify and conduct PoCs where needed 
 
